cff-version: 1.2.0
message: If you use this work, please cite it using the metadata below.
type: dataset
title: L2 Load Latency Test Results Dataset
abstract: This dataset contains results from an experiment measuring network latency
  during L2 load testing on two nodes, nida and cesis. The methodology involved orchestrating
  packet generation using MoonGen with varying rates and sizes to simulate traffic.
  Energy consumption was monitored concurrently as the devices handled these loads
  until externally synchronized termination. Captured logs and measurement data facilitate
  analysis of performance under different configurations.
